    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の企画は、ドーナツ屋の一日店長……\n遙子のは……この間のキャンプね……",
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 4.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3666.6666666,
          "startTime": 8.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "それ、『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の記事\nですよね。mihoさんにもオファーが来たんですか？",
      "startTime": 12.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子の企画にゲストで出演した時\n「ぜひ」って話をいただいたのよ",
      "startTime": 19.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ただの社交辞令かと思ったら\n本当にオファーをもらえるなんてね",
      "startTime": 24.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですね。あ、もしmihoさんも\n誰かゲストを呼ぶなら、私、参加してみたいです",
      "startTime": 31.6679658846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "貴方を……？　随分貪欲なのね\nBIG4なら、仕事には困っていないでしょうに",
      "startTime": 40.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "困っているというか、その……\n単純にmihoさんと一度、お仕事がしてみたくて",
      "startTime": 49.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "経験豊富な先輩ですし、機会があれば\nもっと近くで学ばせてもらいたいと思ってます",
      "startTime": 57.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}